<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Healthtraco - Secure Health Documents</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/global.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" />
  <style>
    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 100px 20px;
      position: relative;
    }
    .hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -50%;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 100vw;
      height: 100%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
      z-index: -1;
    }
    .hero h1 { 
      font-size: 4.5rem; 
      margin-bottom: 20px; 
      font-weight: 800; 
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #60a5fa, #34d399);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      line-height: 1.1;
    }
    .hero p { 
      font-size: 1.25rem; 
      max-width: 650px; 
      margin: 0 auto 40px; 
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }
    .features-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
      gap: 30px;
      padding-bottom: 80px;
      margin-top: -20px;
    }
    .feature-card { 
      text-align: center; 
      padding: 40px 30px;
    }
    .feature-icon {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      color: var(--secondary-light);
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      display: inline-block;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 0 15px rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.4));
    }
    .feature-card h3 { 
      font-size: 1.5rem; 
      margin-bottom: 15px; 
      color: white; 
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero h1 { font-size: 3rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="header animate-slide">
    <div class="container">
      <a href="/" class="logo"><i class="fa-solid fa-shield-heart float-icon"></i> Healthtraco</a>
      <nav class="nav-links">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/login" class="btn btn-outline">Log In</a>
        <a href="/signup" class="btn btn-primary">Sign Up</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container animate-slide delay-1">
        <h1>Your Health Data,<br/>Securely Managed.</h1>
        <p>Upload, store, and access your medical documents safely in our private cloud vault. Your safety is our absolute priority.</p>
        <div class="animate-slide delay-2">
          <a href="/signup" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg" style="font-size: 1.1rem; padding: 16px 36px;">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-user-shield"></i> Get Started Securely
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="container">
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="card feature-card animate-slide delay-1">
          <div class="feature-icon float-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-lock"></i></div>
          <h3>Digital Security First</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">Your sessions are rigorously managed and protected utilizing industry-standard auth methods.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card feature-card animate-slide delay-2">
          <div class="feature-icon float-icon" style="animation-delay: 1s;"><i class="fa-solid fa-file-medical"></i></div>
          <h3>Unlimited Storage</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">We leverage native database grid structures to securely split and store highly confidential reports.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card feature-card animate-slide delay-3">
          <div class="feature-icon float-icon" style="animation-delay: 2s;"><i class="fa-solid fa-laptop-medical"></i></div>
          <h3>Remote Accessibility</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">Whether you're at the hospital or traveling, pull up your life-saving documents in seconds.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="footer animate-slide delay-3">
    <div class="container">
      <p>&copy; 2026 Healthtraco. Your trusted partner in digital health document management.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
